history.text: I have never seen The Social Network is it any good?
Well do you like movies about the rise of powerful peope?
People I mean
Yes I do as long as the movie is good and isn’t boring
Isn’t this movie about Facebook it seems like it might be a little slow
It's about the founding of facebook, so I think it would be fast paced.
It has a lot of good actors in it so I think I might enjoy it I’ll have to give it a try
Do you know if this movie is on Netflix?
I see they have Jesse Eisenberg
Don't know.  I love the director, too.
What other movies has he directed besides the social network?
I don't remember off hand, but it was good.
I see this movie is a biographical drama do you enjoy these types of films?

Oh
 I love biographical dramas
Can you suggest any other biographical dramas that might be interesting that are similar to this movie?
So do you care how critics rate a movie?
No I don’t really care about the ratings on a movie because I have seen a lot of really good movies that had negative ratings and I very much enjoyed them
I wonder when they knew facebook was going to be huge
Yeah I wonder that too. I see this movie was adopted from a book have you read the book?
Only heard of the book right now to be honest
Would you rather read the book before watching this movie or vice versa?
I like to watch movies, skip the book
Have you seen this particular movie? If so is it worth watching?
The more I read, the more I want to see it.
Depositions, so it is kind of a courtroom thriller
It sounds interesting to me as well. It’s kind of funny to see that Facebook was actually originally called face mash and was actually used as a dating website for Harvard students
I’m sure it will be an interesting film to see how Facebook has evolved over the years and the tribulations that Mark Zuckerberg had to go through to get to where he is today
The fact that you get to see how it came together and how the friends fell apart would be compelling.
Definitely, sounds very interesting. Although it is quite sad to think that money and power changed their relationship
I think having friends who just wanted a dating site and then having the thing explode would be crazy.
